=== Overview ===
TryOCaml is the easiest way to learn how to code in OCaml language. A funny way
to learn the language and be in touch with experts through IRC channel.

=== Requirements ===

  * Findlib
  * Js_of_ocaml (version 1.0.3 at least)

=== Try it === 

0: make

Then, with your favorite browser launch src/index.html:

1: chromium-browser src/index.html

